<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="may-might-just-as-well-do-sth">may / might (just) as well do sth</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>做某事也无妨：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Since we haven’t gone very far, we might just as well  turn around to get the map. 
既然我们还没走远，我们不妨返回去取地图。</p><footer>2011 上海改</footer></div></div>